1. install node and npm 

2. istall vscode 

3. install from terminal

npm install -g create-react-app   << to do this step .... simply go to CMD >> AND paste this 
create-react-app --version  << after above step ... type this 

Now... type >> d:  
   in command prompt and make a folder here
   "mkdir reactapplication"
   after that 
   "cd reactapplication"

now finally   do the below step
create-react-app <projectname> 